<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/empower/new/bennett.htm 204.71.237.86 19970108161626 text/html 3632
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:16:39 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 20:48:28 GMT
Content-length: 3444
