http://www.sbsc.org:80/pff/aspen-mv.html 204.71.237.86 19970108165313 text/html 16717
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:53:29 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:21 GMT
