http://www.sbsc.org:80/heritage/p_review/spring95/sympoth.html 204.71.237.86 19970108165546 text/html 17850
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:55:54 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:28 GMT
Content-length: 17663
