http://www.sbsc.org:80/empower/ps-afirm.html 204.71.237.86 19970108165710 text/html 8928
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:57:16 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:54:53 GMT
