HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 17:03:48 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 16-May-96 20:54:01 GMT
Content-length: 5470
Content-type: text/html
