http://www.sbsc.org:80/nationalreview/25sep95/dumdum.htm 204.71.237.86 19970108171333 text/html 8686
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 17:13:50 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:47 GMT
