<center><H2><FONT SIZE="+3">T</font>he <FONT SIZE="+3">W</font>orks of <FONT SIZE="+3">R</font>ussell <FONT SIZE="+3">K</font>irk</H2></center>
<p><center><img alt="_______________________" align="middle"src="divide.gif"></center>
